sequenceDiagram
    participant SG as solve_game()
    participant HSP as HybridSearchPipeline
    participant REG as GameProfileRegistry
    participant CONF as HybridSearchConfig
    participant L1 as DeltaStateBFSEngine
    participant L2 as L2PruningEngine
    participant L3 as L3EvaluationEngine
    participant L4 as L4DecisionEngine
    participant RE as ReplayEngine
    participant KS as KSnapEngine
    participant VER as _verify_plan()

    SG->>HSP: solve(game, "ka59", 0)
    HSP->>REG: get_hybrid_config("ka59")
    REG->>CONF: return ka59_config {l1=WALL_BFS, l2=COMBINATORIAL, l3=DEAD_ZERO_FUSE, l4=KAPPA_SELECTION}
    
    Note over HSP,L1: L1 状态枚举层
    HSP->>L1: _run_l1(game, config, 0)
    L1->>L1: Wall-BFS: bfs_with_wall_priority(game, 0)
    L1->>L1: 每节点: Node(parent_id, action) — 零拷贝
    L1->>L1: 物理检查: can_push_box() + is_deadlock_corner()
    L1->>L1: Dead-Zero熔断: 跳过deadlock节点
    L1-->>HSP: candidates: list[Node]

    Note over HSP,L2: L2 结构剪枝层
    HSP->>L2: _run_l2(candidates, game, config)
    L2->>L2: 组合对称剪枝: 八元数编码旋转/镜像归一化
    L2->>L2: 去重: LayoutHasher.hash_with_shape()
    L2-->>HSP: pruned: list[Node]

    Note over HSP,L3: L3 差评估层
    HSP->>L3: _run_l3(pruned, game, config)
    L3->>RE: replay_batch(pruned_node_ids) → 物化所有候选
    RE->>RE: deepcopy(root_game) + perform_action序列
    L3->>KS: project(eml_state, prior) → (best_v, η)
    L3->>L3: η < δ_K → PASS; η ≥ δ_K → 熔断
    L3-->>HSP: scored: list[ScoredCandidate(node, η, confidence)]

    Note over HSP,L4: L4 κ-优选决策融合
    HSP->>L4: _run_l4(scored, game, config)
    L4->>L4: η升序排序 → confidence = 1 - η/δ_K
    L4->>L4: 选择最小η候选 → 回溯action序列
    L4->>RE: replay(best_node_id) → 物化最优状态
    L4-->>HSP: final_plan: list[tuple]

    HSP->>VER: _verify_plan(final_plan, pristine_game)
    VER->>VER: deepcopy(pristine_game) + replay plan → _is_level_solved()
    VER-->>HSP: True/False

    HSP-->>SG: return final_plan or None